<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="section" id="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="rv">
      <p class="eyebrow">What It Does</p>
      <h2>Seven layers of intelligence,<br/>built for your biology</h2>
      <p class="body-grey" style="max-width:500px;margin-top:8px">Every recommendation Taiuo makes is rooted in your data &mdash; your scan, your lifestyle, your biology.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-grid">

      <!-- Featured card: Skin Intelligence — spans full width with large image -->
      <div class="card fc fc-featured rv d1">
        <div class="fc-content-wrap">
          <div class="fc-icon-box">
            <img src="./public/Skin intelligence new image.webp" alt="Skin Intelligence" width="72" height="72"/>
          </div>
          <h3 class="fc-title">Skin Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="fc-desc">Analyses 25 distinct skin markers from a standard smartphone photo. Detects acne, pigmentation, hydration levels, texture irregularities, and UV damage before they become visible.</p>
          <a href="#" class="fc-link">Explore the technology &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="fc-badge">
          <div class="fc-badge-n">79%</div>
          <div class="fc-badge-l">Detection<br/>Accuracy</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Disease Screening -->
      <div class="card fc rv d2">
        <div class="fc-icon-box">
          <img src="./public/multiple-stars.svg" alt="Disease Screening" width="48" height="48"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title">Disease Screening</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Clinical-grade melanoma and skin cancer screening trained on 60k+ dermatology images, reviewed by board-certified specialists.</p>
        <a href="#" class="fc-link">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Product Intelligence -->
      <div class="card fc rv d3">
        <div class="fc-icon-box">
          <img src="./public/product@2x.png" alt="Product Intelligence" width="48" height="48"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title">Product Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Matches across 200+ products from 25+ brands to your exact skin type, concerns, and budget. No more spending on products that don't work for you.</p>
        <a href="#" class="fc-link">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Lifestyle Sync -->
      <div class="card fc rv d1">
        <div class="fc-icon-box">
          <img src="./public/Frame-1707481743-1@2x.png" alt="Lifestyle Sync" width="48" height="48"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title">Lifestyle Sync</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Correlates sleep, stress biomarkers, hydration, and nutrition with your skin changes. Discovers what your daily habits are actually doing to your appearance.</p>
        <a href="#" class="fc-link">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Progress Tracking -->
      <div class="card fc rv d4">
        <div class="fc-icon-box">
          <img src="./public/chart-data@2x.png" alt="Progress Tracking" width="48" height="48"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title">Progress Tracking</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Weekly skin health scores, monthly transformation reports, and before/after visualisations showing the compound effect of consistent good decisions.</p>
        <a href="#" class="fc-link">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Fragrance Profiling -->
      <div class="card fc rv d2">
        <div class="fc-icon-box">
          <img src="./public/Asset-1-4x-2@2x.png" alt="Fragrance Profiling" width="48" height="48"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title">Fragrance Profiling</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Maps your skin chemistry, hormonal patterns, and environment to recommend fragrances that work with your biology &mdash; not against it.</p>
        <a href="#" class="fc-link">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Diet Recommendations -->
      <div class="card fc rv d3">
        <div class="fc-icon-box">
          <img src="./public/Group-1000005015@2x.png" alt="Personalised Diet Recommendations" width="48" height="48"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title">Personalised Diet Recommendations</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Your skin is a mirror of what you eat. Taiuo analyses your skin data and lifestyle markers to recommend a diet tailored to your biology &mdash; the nutrients, foods, and habits that genuinely improve your skin from the inside out.</p>
        <a href="#" class="fc-link">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section" id="how-it-works" style="background:var(--bg)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="rv">
      <h2>Get your results in 3 easy steps</h2>
      <p class="body-grey" style="max-width:500px;margin:8px 0 0">Simple, fast, and accurate &mdash; discover what your skin is telling you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-grid" style="margin-top:52px">
      <div class="card fc rv d1" style="padding:32px 26px;text-align:center">
        <div class="step-img-wrap" style="height:200px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <img src="./public/face-man2-1@2x.png" alt="Capture skin scan" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title" style="margin-bottom:10px">Capture Your Skin Image</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Take a skin scan using your phone camera. The AI analyses multiple skin markers &mdash; no specialist hardware required.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card fc rv d2" style="padding:32px 26px;text-align:center">
        <div class="step-img-wrap" style="height:200px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <img src="./public/chart-data@2x.png" alt="AI analysis" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title" style="margin-bottom:10px">AI Analysis &amp; Diagnosis</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Your scan is cross-referenced with your lifestyle data and clinical database to produce a personal report within seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card fc rv d3" style="padding:32px 26px;text-align:center">
        <div class="step-img-wrap" style="height:200px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <img src="./public/product@2x.png" alt="Personalised results" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"/>
        </div>
        <h3 class="fc-title" style="margin-bottom:10px">Improve Your Lifestyle</h3>
        <p class="fc-desc">Receive a personalised action plan &mdash; curated products, lifestyle adjustments, and a transformation roadmap built for your biology.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:40px" class="rv d2">
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-red">Start Now &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT / VISION -->
<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="about-grid">

      <div class="img-stack rv">
        <div class="img-b tall">
          <img src="./public/tech_meets_beauty_our_vision_long_image.png" alt="Skincare" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <div class="img-b">
          <img src="./public/our_vision_top right.png" alt="Wellness" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <div class="img-b">
          <img src="./public/our_vision_bottom right.png" alt="Facial care" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-text rv d2">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Vision</p>
        <h2>Lifestyle intelligence that helps people understand themselves &mdash; instantly</h2>
        <p class="body-grey">In a world overflowing with products, trends, and opinions, Taiuo exists to replace guesswork with clarity. Personal care should not be driven by marketing or one-size-fits-all advice. It should be intelligent, adaptive, and personal.</p>
        <div class="about-quote">"Just as conversational AI became the default interface for knowledge, Taiuo becomes the default interface for lifestyle decisions."</div>
        <div class="checks">
          <div class="chk"><div class="chk-dot">&#10003;</div><span>People understanding their skin without confusion or fear</span></div>
          <div class="chk"><div class="chk-dot">&#10003;</div><span>Brands competing on outcomes rather than advertising spend</span></div>
          <div class="chk"><div class="chk-dot">&#10003;</div><span>Personal care that is intelligent, adaptive, and truly individual</span></div>
        </div>
        <div><a href="#" class="btn btn-ghost" style="margin-top:4px">Read our story</a></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

